name: Nordic Eurovision Party 2026
description:
Opplev en unik Eurovision-helg i hjertet av Oslo, med liveopptredener fra noen av Europas mest ikoniske Eurovision-artister:

**Eurovision 2026 artists:**
Tamara Živković (Montenegro 2026)
Satoshi (Moldova 2026)

**Eurovision legends & special guests:**
Elisabeth Andreassen (Sweden 1982, Norway 1985, 1994, 1996)
Olsen Brothers (Jørgen Olsen, Denmark 2000)
Poli Genova (Bulgaria 2011, 2016)
Guri Schanke (Norway 2006)
Ovi (Romania 2010, 2014)
Ilinca (Romania 2017)
Lindsay Dracass (United Kingdom 2001)

**Nordic & MGP special guests:**
Mathilde SPZ (MGP Norway 2024)

Gjennom helgen blir det flere arrangementer i Oslo for deg som vil gjøre litt ekstra ut av opplevelsen. Fredag kveld inviterer vi til en avslappet mingle-fest, mer info kommer. Etter konserten fortsetter festen på den offisielle afterpartyen.

Dette er bare starten, flere artister annonseres frem mot mars 2026!

--

Welcome to Nordic Eurovision Party!

Nordic Eurovision Party brings Eurovision artists from all around Europe to Oslo to promote their songs ahead of the contest in May. The show also features legendary names from Eurovision history, combined with a strong Nordic feel-good vibe.

**Eurovision 2026 artists:**
Tamara Živković (Montenegro 2026)
Satoshi (Moldova 2026)

**Eurovision legends & special guests:**
Elisabeth Andreassen (Sweden 1982, Norway 1985, 1994, 1996)
Olsen Brothers (Jørgen Olsen, Denmark 2000)
Poli Genova (Bulgaria 2011, 2016)
Guri Schanke (Norway 2006)
Ovi (Romania 2010, 2014)
Ilinca (Romania 2017)
Lindsay Dracass (United Kingdom 2001)

**Nordic & MGP special guests:**
Mathilde SPZ (MGP Norway 2024)

More Eurovision 2026 artists will be announced continuously as we get closer to March 21st.

Experience a full weekend in the Eurovision universe with concerts, fan meet-ups and official side events. Find the latest updates at www.nordiceurovision.com

Secure your ticket now – see you in Oslo!

--
